    <div class="wrapper">

        <article class="content-area">

            <h2>Advancing Cardinal<br> Hayes High School</h2>

            <div class="content-data">


                <img src="" />
                <p>Beginning in 2009, Cardinal Hayes was made an independent school from the Archdiocese. While the Archdiocese remains committed to the success of CHHS, they are unable to provide the kind of financial support they once did. With this backdrop, we announce: Forever Hayes, The Comprehensive Campaign for Cardinal Hayes High School.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-842" src="https://alumni.cardinalhayes.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/archdiocese-table.png" alt="archdiocese-table" width="727" height="259" /></p>
<h4>Diminishing Support</h4>
<p>Hayes can no longer count on Archdiocese support for operations.</p>
                        <!-- <div class="copy">
                            <p>Thank you for considering a gift to Cardinal Hayes. The generosity of our alumni and friends has a tangible and direct impact on the work of Hayes&#039; faculty and students.</p>
<p>All gifts are tax deductible. All online gifts are made through a secure server and generate an e-mail confirmation as well as a gift receipt through the mail.</p>
                        </div> -->
                                </div>
        </article>

                    <aside class="sidebar-area">
                <ul id="right-sidebar-section" class="right-sidebar-section">  
                    <li id="ctatext-4" class="widget-class call-to-action-widget">						
		
						
			
